Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.44,0:02:16.40,utaware def,,0,0,0,,Oh, Kuuya-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.40,0:02:19.24,utaware def,,0,0,0,,This is too much for me after all!
